Setting Potting Theme

## Plotting theme
theme_fancy <- function() {
  theme_bw() +
    theme(
      text = element_text(family = "Helvetica"),
      axis.text = element_text(size = 8, color = "black"),
      axis.title = element_text(size = 10, color = "black"),
      axis.line.x = element_line(size = 0.3, color = "black"),
      axis.line.y = element_line(size = 0.3, color = "black"),
      axis.ticks = element_line(size = 0.3, color = "black"),
      panel.border = element_blank(),
      panel.grid.major.x = element_blank(),
      panel.grid.minor.x = element_blank(),
      panel.grid.minor.y = element_blank(),
      panel.grid.major.y = element_blank(),
      plot.margin = unit(c(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 0.5), units = , "cm"),
      plot.title = element_text(
        size = 10,
        vjust = 1,
        hjust = 0.5,
        color = "black"
      ),
      legend.text = element_text(size = 9, color = "black"),
      legend.title = element_text(size = 9, color = "black"),
      legend.position = c(0.9, 0.9),
      legend.key.size = unit(0.7, "line"),
      legend.background = element_rect(
        color = "black",
        fill = "transparent",
        size = 2,
        linetype = "blank"
      )
    )
}

Group mangroves by year

agg_tbl <- df1 %>% group_by(year) %>% summarise(Total_Mangroves=sum(Mangroves),.groups = 'drop')
agg_tbl

Convert to a new dataframe

df2 <- agg_tbl %>% as.data.frame()
df2

df2$Total_Mangroves_Hectares <- df2$Total_Mangroves / 10000
df2

Drop Total_Mangroves columns as unnesessary

df2 = subset(df2,select = -c(Total_Mangroves))
df2

Duplicate dataset

df3 <- df2

Create a Line plot showing a time-series for Lamu County and Manda


p1 <- ggplot(data=df8, aes(x=year, y=Total_Mangroves_Hectares)) +
    geom_line() +
    geom_point() +
  theme_fancy() +
  ylim(lamu_y_axis_min,lamu_y_axis_max) +
  ggtitle("Lamu County") +
  xlab("Year") +
  ylab("Hectares of Mangroves")

p2 <- ggplot(data=df7, aes(x=year, y=Total_Mangroves_Hectares)) +
    geom_line() +
    geom_point() +
  theme_fancy() +
  ylim(manda_y_axis_min, manda_y_axis_max) +
  ggtitle("MICP") +
  xlab("Year") +
  ylab("Hectares of Mangroves")

p3 <- ggplot(data=df8, aes(x=year, y=Total_Mangroves_Hectares)) +
    geom_bar(stat="identity") +
  theme_fancy() +
  ggtitle("Lamu County") +
  xlab("Year") +
  ylab("Hectares of Mangroves")

p4 <- ggplot(data=df7, aes(x=year, y=Total_Mangroves_Hectares)) +
    geom_bar(stat="identity") +
  theme_fancy() +
  ggtitle("MICP") +
  xlab("Year") +
  ylab("Hectares of Mangroves")

fig2 <- p1 + p2 + p3 + p4 + plot_annotation(tag_levels = 'a') + 
  plot_annotation(title = 'Lamu County and MICP mangrove cover 1996 to 2020',
                  theme = theme(plot.title = element_text(size = 16)))
